384
00:19:16,755 --> 00:19:18,323
Come on, I wanna see.

385
00:19:18,824 --> 00:19:21,793
The one in green is Ryuki,
and the one in red is Bomi.

386
00:19:21,860 --> 00:19:23,862
- One of them?
- It's one of them, yeah.

387
00:19:23,929 --> 00:19:25,230
The one in green, then.

388
00:19:25,297 --> 00:19:26,431
Red, the one in red.

389
00:19:26,498 --> 00:19:27,933
- In red! But…
- It's Bomi.

390
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,034
- Bomi.
- Oh, I see.

391
00:19:29,101 --> 00:19:32,204
So, why him? What do you like about him?

392
00:19:32,271 --> 00:19:36,341
Well, you know,
in fact, before we met here this time…

393
00:19:36,408 --> 00:19:37,709
You knew him?

394
00:19:37,776 --> 00:19:40,145
We went out to dinner once last year.

395
00:19:40,212 --> 00:19:42,614
- Oh.
- Did you approach him back then?

396
00:19:42,681 --> 00:19:43,782
Well, he did.

397
00:19:43,849 --> 00:19:44,816
Hmm!

398
00:19:45,317 --> 00:19:46,952
That's such a popular guy thing.

399
00:19:47,019 --> 00:19:49,188
- I'm not popular.
- No, that's seriously amazing.

400
00:19:49,254 --> 00:19:50,656
Of course you're popular.

401
00:19:51,557 --> 00:19:54,626
Anyway, after a year,

402
00:19:55,627 --> 00:19:57,029
