410
00:20:13,011 --> 00:20:16,048
- I've gone on two.
- You've gone on two? Wow!

411
00:20:19,151 --> 00:20:20,652
- He's having fun.
- He has great friends.

412
00:20:20,719 --> 00:20:23,222
- The ladies are excited. That's nice.
- It's nice.

413
00:20:23,288 --> 00:20:24,656
He has fun friends.

414
00:20:24,723 --> 00:20:29,261
I told him, "I said before
I was interested in you, but recently,

415
00:20:29,328 --> 00:20:33,665
I realized there might be a little
