455
00:22:27,446 --> 00:22:30,682
- <i>She's so funny!</i>
- <i>Good line. "Set the standard."</i>

456
00:22:30,749 --> 00:22:32,918
Is he the kind of person
you can talk with?

457
00:22:32,984 --> 00:22:36,054
- Yeah, I think so.
